{{!-- Decorative black mask over a demo-mosaic clip's burnt-in lower-left
      caption, carrying the clean canonical title. Shared by the gallery tile and
      the item detail viewer so both surfaces render the identical correction
      from the same media record. The title also appears as real page text
      nearby (the tile caption / the detail heading), so the mask is aria-hidden
      to avoid a duplicate screen-reader announcement, and pointer-events are
      disabled in CSS so it never intercepts player interaction. --}}
<span class="gallery-tile-caption-mask" aria-hidden="true">{{caption}}</span>
